::Zardus/Prowl/Zenyak::

Zardus recieves Zergling's message. "Yes," he replies over the comm-link, 
"Please go on a perimiter patroll. If you see Ominous trying to enter the 
base, kill him. Any one else, report to me."

He stands up and walks out of the base, flying off towards Nemesis.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Prowl lands near the Ark, putting Zenyak down near the shields. He turns 
around and looks at the water seperating him from the mainland. He'd probably 
need to carry Iron Raptor across again.

He takes several steps toward the edge of the island, but stumbles, feeling 
lightheaded. He transforms into robot mode and looks down at his shoulder. 
The wound that Iron Raptor had treated had stopped dripping, but the other 
one was still spewing mech fluid. Prowl shruggs. He could always go to a CR 
chamber later.

Prowl flies across to the mainland, waiting for Iron Raptor to get there.
